[{"phelps":"ABU0009","text":"## Oktavuohta\n\nO Don láđisváimmot hearrá, Don Guhte leat addálas ja návccalaš. Mii leat Du bálvaleaddjit Du sállemuša vuorddekeahtes árpmu suojis. Atte midjiide Du geahčastaga skeaŋkka. Atte čuovgga čalmmiidasamet, gulu beljiidasamet ja ipmárdusa ja ráhkisvuođa váimmuidasamet. Daga sillomet ilolažžan ja lihkolažžan Du ilu sivdnádusaid bokte. O Hearrá! Čájet midjiide Du gonagasgotti luotta ja virkkosmahte buohkaid Du bassi vuoiŋŋa vuoiŋŋanasaiguin. Atte midjiide agálaš eallima ja nohkameahttun gudni. Ovttas olmmošgotti ja illudahte olmmošlaš máilmmi. Čuovvot mii buohkat Du luotta, áibbašeatnot Du miellabuori ja ohccot Du gonagasgotti suollemasvuođaid. O Ipmil! Ovttas ja čana oktii váibmomet Du nohkameahttun báttiin. Duođalaččat Don leat váibmoláđis ja buotveagalaš.","name":"Oktavuohta","category":"Oktavuohta","order_in_cat":1,"source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"1217393e-8903-4622-b691-5aa4f214cd64","translations":[{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"lo","lang_name":"Lao"},{"language":"sm","lang_name":"Samoan"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"}]},{"phelps":"AB11094","text":"## Váinniid beales\n\nO Ipmilan! Don suttuid ándagassii addi, skeaŋkkaid juohkki, váttisvuođaid eret váldi! Duođalaččat, mun bivddán Du addit suttuid ándagassii daidda, geat leat guođđán eatnanlaš orrunsajiset ja sirdásan vuoiŋŋalaš máilbmái. O Hearrán! Buhtis sin váivviin, váldde eret sin morrašeaset ja nuppástuhte sin sevdnjesvuođa čuovgan. Suova sin lávket lihku šaddogárdái, basa sin buhttásamos čáziin ja divtte sin geahčadit Du šerresvuođa alimus vári alde.","name":"Váinniid beales","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"1a22a8c8-2b24-49d5-a116-02945030a8ec","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"bn","lang_name":"Bengali"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"hr","lang_name":"Croatian"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"gux","lang_name":"Gourmanchéma"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"ik","lang_name":"Inupiaq"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"naq","lang_name":"Khoekhoegowab"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"kgf","lang_name":"Kube"},{"language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"language":"sxn","lang_name":"Low Saxon"},{"language":"mg","lang_name":"Malagasy"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"mt","lang_name":"Maltese"},{"language":"mr","lang_name":"Marathi"},{"language":"mh","lang_name":"Marshallese"},{"language":"ne","lang_name":"Nepali"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"kj","lang_name":"Oshikwanyama"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"diu","lang_name":"Rugciriku"},{"language":"sr","lang_name":"Serbian"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"sl","lang_name":"Slovenian"},{"language":"st","lang_name":"Southern Sotho"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"srn","lang_name":"Sranan Tongo"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"te","lang_name":"Telugu"},{"language":"tet","lang_name":"Tetum"},{"language":"ur","lang_name":"Urdu"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"ABU0129EDU","text":"## Mánát\n\nO Ipmil! Čuvge dáid mánáid. Dát mánát leat Du heđengárddi šattut, Du niittu rásit, Du\n\nšaddogárddi ruvssut. Divtte arvvát láktadit sin; atte Duohtavuođa Beaivváža ráhkisvuođainat báitit sin ala. Divtte Vuoiŋŋanasat virkkosmahttit sin nu, ahte sii ahtanuššet, šaddet ja ovdánit ja čuvget geažehis čábbodagas. Don leat árvvas. Don leat láđisváimmot.","name":"Mánát","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"27728891-fcdd-442a-a4f0-8854b6343858","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ceb","lang_name":"Cebuano"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"co","lang_name":"Corsican"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"fo","lang_name":"Faroese"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"haw","lang_name":"Hawaiian"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"language":"mg","lang_name":"Malagasy"},{"language":"mr","lang_name":"Marathi"},{"language":"mh","lang_name":"Marshallese"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"cnr","lang_name":"Montenegrin"},{"language":"nal","lang_name":"Nalik"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"kj","lang_name":"Oshikwanyama"},{"language":"pap","lang_name":"Papiamento"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"fa-translit","lang_name":"Persian (Latin)"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"diu","lang_name":"Rugciriku"},{"language":"sm","lang_name":"Samoan"},{"language":"sr","lang_name":"Serbian"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"st","lang_name":"Southern Sotho"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"te","lang_name":"Telugu"},{"language":"tet","lang_name":"Tetum"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"}]},{"phelps":"BB00001KNO","text":"## Geahččalusat ja váttisvuođat\n\nSon lea láđisváimmot, buotveagalaš! O Ipmil, mu Ipmilan! Don oainnát mu, Don dovddat mu; Don leat Albmán ja Báhtaranbáikán. In geange leat mun ohcalan, inge ovttage mun ohcal; in mange bálgá leat mun johtán, inge ovttage bálgá boađe johtit earet Du ráhkisvuođa bálgá. Sevdnjes doaivvuhisvuođa ijas mu čalbmi jorggiha vuordevažžan ja dievva doaivvu Du geažehis buorrevuođa guvlui ja veiggodettiin Du čábbodaga ja dievaslašvuođa muitin virkkosmahttá ja gievrrasmahttá mu goldnan sielu. Vaikke leage dušše goaikkanas; dat, gean Du árpmu viiddisvuohta veahkeha, šaddá geažis áhpin. Ja smávimus atoma, man Du láđisváimmot ustitlašvuohta veahkeha boahtá báitit šearradamos nástin. Govčča Du suodjalussii, O Don buhtisvuođa Vuoigŋa, Don guhte leat Buotveagalaš Sállejeaddji, dán ráhkisvuođa šláva, čuvgejuvvon bálvaleaddját. Veahket su dán leahkima máilmmis bissut nanusin Du ráhkisvuođas ja atte dán lámissoajat lotti gávdnat báhtaransaji ja dorvvu Du ipmillaš beasis, almmálaš muora suojis.","name":"Geahččalusat ja váttisvuođat","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"edc30ae0-4833-4ce8-8f19-100973dfd14d","translations":[{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"lb","lang_name":"Luxembourgish"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"sr","lang_name":"Serbian"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"}]},{"phelps":"BB00018ADJ","text":"## Geahččalusat ja váttisvuođat\n\nMun ohcalan Du Fámut bokte, O Ipmilan. Ale divtte mange ráfehuhttit mu geahččalusaid áigge, ja berošmeahttunvuođa bottuin oahpis lávkkiidan deaivat Du movttiidusa čađa. Don leat Ipmil, buotveagalaš leat Don dahkat dan, maid Don háliidat. Ii oktage sáhte vuostálastit Du Dáhtu iige Du Áigumuša.","name":"Geahččalusat ja váttisvuođat","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"42251e3f-e7b0-48bd-a924-7ae12b11c821","translations":[{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"ceb","lang_name":"Cebuano"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"hi","lang_name":"Hindi"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"mt","lang_name":"Maltese"},{"language":"mi","lang_name":"Maori"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"fa-translit","lang_name":"Persian (Latin)"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"sr","lang_name":"Serbian"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"sl","lang_name":"Slovenian"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"tet","lang_name":"Tetum"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"}]},{"phelps":"BB00623","text":"## Geahččalusat ja váttisvuođat\n\nLii-uv kihheen eres vädisvuođâi meddâl välddee, ko Immeel. Eeđâ, pajedum, liävus Immeel. Sun lii Immeel. Puohah laa Suu palvâleijeeh já puohah vuáláneh Suu táátun.","name":"Geahččalusat ja váttisvuođat","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"2d98fd7c-ffa5-4cce-8c0c-d863cff01acd","translations":[{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"language":"ar-translit","lang_name":"Arabic (Latin)"},{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"sne","lang_name":"Bau Bidayuh"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"bn","lang_name":"Bengali"},{"language":"bla","lang_name":"Blackfoot"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"km","lang_name":"Central Khmer"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"ny","lang_name":"Chichewa"},{"language":"chn","lang_name":"Chinook Jargon"},{"language":"co","lang_name":"Corsican"},{"language":"hr","lang_name":"Croatian"},{"language":"cs","lang_name":"Czech"},{"language":"dgz","lang_name":"Daga"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"fo","lang_name":"Faroese"},{"language":"fj","lang_name":"Fijian"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"gux","lang_name":"Gourmanchéma"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"gu","lang_name":"Gujarati"},{"language":"ha","lang_name":"Hausa"},{"language":"haw","lang_name":"Hawaiian"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"hi","lang_name":"Hindi"},{"language":"ho","lang_name":"Hiri Motu"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"iba","lang_name":"Iban"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"ik","lang_name":"Inupiaq"},{"language":"ga","lang_name":"Irish"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"kiw","lang_name":"Kiwai"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"ksd","lang_name":"Kuanua"},{"language":"kgf","lang_name":"Kube"},{"language":"dih","lang_name":"Kumiai"},{"language":"lkt","lang_name":"Lakota"},{"language":"lo","lang_name":"Lao"},{"language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"language":"lb","lang_name":"Luxembourgish"},{"language":"mg","lang_name":"Malagasy"},{"language":"ms","lang_name":"Malay"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"mi","lang_name":"Maori"},{"language":"mr","lang_name":"Marathi"},{"language":"mh","lang_name":"Marshallese"},{"language":"moh","lang_name":"Mohawk"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"cnr","lang_name":"Montenegrin"},{"language":"meu","lang_name":"Motu"},{"language":"nal","lang_name":"Nalik"},{"language":"nv","lang_name":"Navajo"},{"language":"ne","lang_name":"Nepali"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"one","lang_name":"Oneida"},{"language":"pap","lang_name":"Papiamento"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"diu","lang_name":"Rugciriku"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"sm","lang_name":"Samoan"},{"language":"sr","lang_name":"Serbian"},{"language":"zh-Hans","lang_name":"Simplified Chinese"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"sl","lang_name":"Slovenian"},{"language":"st","lang_name":"Southern Sotho"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"srn","lang_name":"Sranan Tongo"},{"language":"sw","lang_name":"Swahili"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"tk","lang_name":"Turkmen"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"wam","lang_name":"Wampanoag"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"BH00009SER","text":"## Eahket\n\nO Ipmil, mu hearrá, háluidan ulbmil! Dát Du bálvaleaddji ohcala oađđit Du árpmu suojis ja vuoiŋŋastit Du čábbodaga suoji vuolde ja átnut Du várjalusa ja suodjalusa. Bivddán Du, O Hearrán, Du čalmmiidatguin, mat eai oađe, várjalit čalmmiidan oaidnimis eará go Du. Nanusmahte dasto sin čalmmiid, ahte sii oainnašedje Du mearkkaid ja doalahivčče Du almmustuhttima almmiravdda. Don leat Dat, gean buotveagalašvuođa almmustusaid ovddas fámuin stuorimusatge leat dorggiidan. Ii leat mihkkige eará Ipmiliid go Don, Buotveagalaš, Buot siskkimuš leahkin, Eavttuheapmi.","name":"Eahket","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"192ea94f-f253-4b72-b9df-76b0ca90da0e","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"bn","lang_name":"Bengali"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"hr","lang_name":"Croatian"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gux","lang_name":"Gourmanchéma"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"haw","lang_name":"Hawaiian"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"naq","lang_name":"Khoekhoegowab"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"language":"lt","lang_name":"Lithuanian"},{"language":"mg","lang_name":"Malagasy"},{"language":"med","lang_name":"Melpa"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"cnr","lang_name":"Montenegrin"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"kj","lang_name":"Oshikwanyama"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"diu","lang_name":"Rugciriku"},{"language":"sr","lang_name":"Serbian"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"ur","lang_name":"Urdu"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"BH00009SHE","text":"## Iđit\n\nMun lean lihkkan Du suodjalusas, o Ipmilan, ja dat guhte duon dorvvu ohcá galgáge orodit Du suodjalusa bassi lanjas ja Du várjalusa muvrraid siste. Čuovgga siellun Du almmustusa iđitgukso čuovggain nugo du addálasvuođa iđitčuovga čuovggai olgguldas hápmán.","name":"Iđit","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"5a4436ba-8974-4795-803b-0c7ba7b0cb52","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"language":"ar-translit","lang_name":"Arabic (Latin)"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"sne","lang_name":"Bau Bidayuh"},{"language":"be","l